snippet.title: [NEW GAME] Kingdom of EXPLORERS Trailer
snippet.description:
Kingdom of EXPLORERS is an adventure RPG game for up to 2 players.
Each player needs to explore, collect, manage shared resources to unlock new terrains,
upgrade weapons to defeat the enemies, Bosses and save the Dwarves Hidden Island!

STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2306080/Kingdom_of_EXPLORERS/
